$OpenBSD: patch-Makefile_in,v 1.2 2018/12/04 15:49:34 jca Exp $

GCC (4.9, 6.4) does not accept -Wl without argument; use the version
script to hide private symbols like done on Linux.

Index: Makefile.in
--- Makefile.in.orig
+++ Makefile.in
